#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-np17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. HTML: </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:0.3"
msgid "Nissaggiyakaṇḍa"
msgstr "The chapter on relinquishment"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:0.4"
msgid "Kosiyavagga"
msgstr "Monks’ Relinquishment"

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:0.5"
msgid "17. Eḷakalomadhovāpanasikkhāpada"
msgstr "17. The training rule on getting wool washed"

#. HTML: </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-vp-pli3.235, pts-cs-bu-np17.1, pts-vp-en2.94, ms1V_2189
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the Sakyan country at Kapilavatthu in the Banyan Tree Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū bhikkhunīhi eḷakalomāni dhovāpentipi rajāpentipi vijaṭāpentipi."
msgstr "At that time the monks from the group of six got nuns to wash, dye, and comb wool."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.3"
msgid "Bhikkhuniyo eḷakalomāni dhovantiyo rajantiyo vijaṭentiyo riñcanti uddesaṃ paripucchaṃ adhisīlaṃ adhicittaṃ adhipaññaṃ."
msgstr "Because of this work, the nuns neglected recitation, enquiry, the higher morality, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho mahāpajāpati gotamī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "Mahāpajāpati Gotamī then approached the Master,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.5"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr "bowed down to him, and stood to one side."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.6"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ kho mahāpajāpatiṃ gotamiṃ bhagavā etadavoca—"
msgstr "And the Master said to her,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.7"
msgid "“kacci, gotami, bhikkhuniyo appamattā ātāpiniyo pahitattā viharantī”ti?"
msgstr "“Gotamī, I hope the nuns are heedful, energetic, and diligent?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-en2.95
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.8"
msgid "“Kuto, bhante, bhikkhunīnaṃ appamādo."
msgstr "“How, Venerable Sir, could the nuns be heedful?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.9"
msgid "Ayyā chabbaggiyā bhikkhunīhi eḷakalomāni dhovāpentipi rajāpentipi vijaṭāpentipi."
msgstr "And she told him what was happening."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.10"
msgid "Bhikkhuniyo eḷakalomāni dhovantiyo rajantiyo vijaṭentiyo riñcanti uddesaṃ paripucchaṃ adhisīlaṃ adhicittaṃ adhipaññan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2, ms1V_2190
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.11"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā mahāpajāpatiṃ gotamiṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi."
msgstr "The Master then instructed, inspired, and gladdened her with a teaching."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.12"
msgid "Atha kho mahāpajāpati gotamī bhagavatā dhammiyā kathāya sandassitā samādapitā samuttejitā sampahaṃsitā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi."
msgstr "She bowed down to him, circumambulated him with her right side towards him, and departed."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, ms1V_2191
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.13"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etasmiṃ nidāne etasmiṃ pakaraṇe bhikkhusaṃghaṃ sannipātāpetvā chabbaggiye bhikkhū paṭipucchi—"
msgstr "Soon afterwards the Master had the Order assembled and questioned the monks from the group of six:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.14"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, bhikkhunīhi eḷakalomāni dhovāpethapi rajāpethapi vijaṭāpethapī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that you do this?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.15"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.16"
msgid "“Ñātikāyo tumhākaṃ, bhikkhave, aññātikāyo”ti?"
msgstr "“Are they your relatives?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.17"
msgid "“Aññātikāyo, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“No, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.18"
msgid "“Aññātakā, moghapurisā, aññātikānaṃ na jānanti patirūpaṃ vā appatirūpaṃ vā pāsādikaṃ vā apāsādikaṃ vā."
msgstr "“Foolish men, people who are not related don’t know what’s appropriate and what’s inappropriate in dealing with each other, what’s inspiring behavior and what’s not."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.19"
msgid "Tattha nāma tumhe, moghapurisā, aññātikāhi bhikkhunīhi eḷakalomāni dhovāpessathapi rajāpessathapi vijaṭāpessathapi."
msgstr "And still you got unrelated nuns to wash, dye, and comb wool."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.20"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisā, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.21"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.21a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc4, ms1V_2192
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.22"
msgid "“Yo pana bhikkhu aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā eḷakalomāni dhovāpeyya vā rajāpeyya vā vijaṭāpeyya vā, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr "‘If a monk gets an unrelated nun to wash, dye, or comb wool, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.22a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.23"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.24"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. HTML: </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.25"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.26"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr "… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.27"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc6, pts-vp-en2.96, ms1V_2194
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.28"
msgid "Aññātikā nāma"
msgstr "Unrelated:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.29"
msgid "mātito vā pitito vā yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā asambaddhā."
msgstr "anyone who is not a descendant of one’s male ancestors going back seven generations, either on the mother’s side or on the father’s side."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc7, ms1V_2195
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.30"
msgid "Bhikkhunī nāma"
msgstr "A nun:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.31"
msgid "ubhatosaṃghe upasampannā."
msgstr "she has been given the full ordination by both Orders."

#. HTML: </span></p><hr><p>
#. REF: sc8, pts-vp-pli3.236, ms1V_2196
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.32"
msgid "Dhovāti āṇāpeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he tells her to wash it, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.33"
msgid "Dhotāni nissaggiyāni honti."
msgstr "When it has been washed, it becomes subject to relinquishment."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.34"
msgid "Rajāti āṇāpeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he tells her to dye it, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.35"
msgid "Rattāni nissaggiyāni honti."
msgstr "When it has been dyed, it becomes subject to relinquishment."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.36"
msgid "Vijaṭehīti āṇāpeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he tells her to comb it, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.37"
msgid "Vijaṭitāni nissaggiyāni honti."
msgstr "When it has been combed, it becomes subject to relinquishment."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.38"
msgid "Nissajjitabbāni saṃghassa vā gaṇassa vā puggalassa vā."
msgstr "The wool should be relinquished to an Order, a group, or an individual."

#. HTML: <span class="kamma"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.39"
msgid "Evañca pana, bhikkhave, nissajjitabbāni …"
msgstr "“And, monks, it should be relinquished in this way. …"

#. HTML: <span class="pe"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.40"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr "To be expanded as in [Relinquishment 1, paragraphs 13–17](pli-tv-bu-vb-np1#13), with appropriate substitutions. "

#. HTML: </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.41"
msgid "“imāni me, bhante, eḷakalomāni aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā dhovāpitāni nissaggiyāni."
msgstr "‘Venerables, this wool which I got washed by an unrelated nun is to be relinquished."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.42"
msgid "Imānāhaṃ saṃghassa nissajjāmī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "I relinquish it to the Order.’ …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.43"
msgid "dadeyyāti … pe …"
msgstr "the Order should give …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.44"
msgid "dadeyyunti … pe …"
msgstr "you should give …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.45"
msgid "āyasmato dammīti."
msgstr "‘I give this wool back to you.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.45a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc9, ms1V_2197
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.46"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni dhovāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to wash wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.47"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni dhovāpeti rajāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to wash and dye wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and one offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.48"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni dhovāpeti vijaṭāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to wash and comb wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and one offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.49"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni dhovāpeti rajāpeti vijaṭāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to wash, dye, and comb wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and two offenses of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10, ms1V_2198
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.50"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni rajāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to dye wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

#. REF: pts-vp-en2.97
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.51"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni rajāpeti vijaṭāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to dye and comb wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and one offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.52"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni rajāpeti dhovāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to dye and wash wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and one offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.53"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni rajāpeti vijaṭāpeti dhovāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to dye, comb, and wash wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and two offenses of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11, ms1V_2199
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.54"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni vijaṭāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to comb wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.55"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni vijaṭāpeti dhovāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to comb and wash wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and one offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.56"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni vijaṭāpeti rajāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to comb and dye wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and one offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.57"
msgid "Aññātikāya aññātikasaññī eḷakalomāni vijaṭāpeti dhovāpeti rajāpeti, nissaggiyena āpatti dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ."
msgstr "If she is unrelated and he perceives her as unrelated, and he gets her to comb, wash, and dye wool, he commits one offense entailing relinquishment and two offenses of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12, ms1V_2200
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.58"
msgid "Aññātikāya vematiko … pe …"
msgstr "If she is unrelated, but he is unsure if she is …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.59"
msgid "aññātikāya ñātikasaññī … pe …"
msgstr "If she is unrelated, but he perceives her as related …"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.60"
msgid "aññassa eḷakalomāni dhovāpeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he gets her to wash wool belonging to someone else, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.61"
msgid "Ekato upasampannāya dhovāpeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he gets a nun who is fully ordained only on one side to do the washing, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.62"
msgid "Ñātikāya aññātikasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is related, but he perceives her as unrelated, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.63"
msgid "Ñātikāya vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If she is related, but he is unsure if she is, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.64"
msgid "Ñātikāya ñātikasaññī, anāpatti."
msgstr "If she is related and he perceives her as related, there is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.64a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc13, ms1V_2201
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.65"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

#. REF: pts-vp-en2.98
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.66"
msgid "ñātikāya dhovantiyā aññātikā dutiyā hoti,"
msgstr "if a related nun does the washing and an unrelated nun helps her;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.67"
msgid "avuttā dhovati,"
msgstr "if a nun does the washing without being asked;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.68"
msgid "aparibhuttaṃ katabhaṇḍaṃ dhovāpeti,"
msgstr "if he gets a nun to wash an unused and finished article;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.69"
msgid "sikkhamānāya"
msgstr "if it is a trainee nun;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.70"
msgid "sāmaṇeriyā"
msgstr "if it is a novice nun;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.71"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.72"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. HTML: </p><hr><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc14, ms1V_2202
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np17:1.73"
msgid "Eḷakalomadhovāpanasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr "The seventh rule, the training rule on getting wool washed, is finished."
